Message.SourceString: You just walked right past the Wise Old Man there. Best go back and say hi, eh?
Message.LocalizedString: You just walked right past the Wise Old Man there. Best go back and say hi, eh?

Message.SourceString: Here, something to reward your effort.
Message.LocalizedString: Here, something to reward your effort.

Message.SourceString: You'll want to get to grips with gathering and crafting first, Doric can help you with that.
Message.LocalizedString: You'll want to get to grips with gathering and crafting first, Doric can help you with that.

Message.SourceString: You'll find them outside the temple. Check your map if you get lost, but he should be easy to spot.
Message.LocalizedString: You'll find them outside the temple. Check your map if you get lost, but he should be easy to spot.

Message.SourceString: He's the only dwarf on the continent, that we know of anyway, can't miss him.
Message.LocalizedString: He's the only dwarf on the continent, that we know of anyway, can't miss him.

Message.SourceString: Welcome to Ashenfall, sorry about the mess. Had a bit of a dragon problem, that's why we've called for you.
Message.LocalizedString: Welcome to Ashenfall, sorry about the mess. Had a bit of a dragon problem, that's why we've called for you.

Message.SourceString: You've come at a great time. Heroic opportunities await. This long-forgotten place is just screaming to be explored.
Message.LocalizedString: You've come at a great time. Heroic opportunities await. This long-forgotten place is just screaming to be explored.

Message.SourceString: Ah, the new recuit, pleasure to meet you. I'm Doric, smith and general handydwarf of this humble expedition.
Message.LocalizedString: Ah, the new recuit, pleasure to meet you. I'm Doric, smith and general handydwarf of this humble expedition.

Message.SourceString: I won't beat around the bush, it's all hands on deck here and right now you're just not equipped for the job.
Message.LocalizedString: I won't beat around the bush, it's all hands on deck here and right now you're just not equipped for the job.

Message.SourceString: You'll want to build yourself a workbench. Then once you've done that craft yourself a logging axe.
Message.LocalizedString: You'll want to build yourself a workbench. Then once you've done that craft yourself a logging axe.

Message.SourceString: Both require stone and ash logs, which you'll find scattered all over the ground around here.
Message.LocalizedString: Both require stone and ash logs, which you'll find scattered all over the ground around here.

Message.SourceString: Both require stone and ash logs, which you'll find scattered all over the ground around here.
Message.LocalizedString: Both require stone and ash logs, which you'll find scattered all over the ground around here.

Message.SourceString: You'll want to build yourself a workbench. Then once you've done that craft yourself a logging axe.
Message.LocalizedString: You'll want to build yourself a workbench. Then once you've done that craft yourself a logging axe.

Message.SourceString: Now, go chat with Zanik next, the friendly little green lass on the other side of the path by that tent. She'll teach you how to build a shelter.
Message.LocalizedString: Now, go chat with Zanik next, the friendly little green lass on the other side of the path by that tent. She'll teach you how to build a shelter.

Message.SourceString: Ashenfall is a dangerous place, but one full of opportunity. Make sure you take the time to explore it properly.
Message.LocalizedString: Ashenfall is a dangerous place, but one full of opportunity. Make sure you take the time to explore it properly.

Message.SourceString: Ashenfall is a dangerous place, but one full of opportunity. Make sure you take the time to explore it properly.
Message.LocalizedString: Ashenfall is a dangerous place, but one full of opportunity. Make sure you take the time to explore it properly.

Message.SourceString: Aye, that's a fine axe you got there, but even the best tools break over time. When that happens use a crafting bench to repair your gear.
Message.LocalizedString: Aye, that's a fine axe you got there, but even the best tools break over time. When that happens use a crafting bench to repair your gear.
